Or activate it later on an existing collection through the [collection update](#update-collection-parameters.md) API:

```http
PATCH /collections/{collection_name}
{
    "strict_mode_config": {
        "enabled": true,
        "unindexed_filtering_retrieve": false
    }
}
```

